{"tid":585630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小妹而家好徬徨","createTime":"2018-03-09T00:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T06:01:38.000Z","uid":38293,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9bae9bc21ebe5181f9872dadb83b5d2831e69ed1","tid":585630,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"話說尋日我阿叔結婚，咁我老豆當然會飲大咗啦！<br />\n本來都無咩<br />\n<br />\n直接尋晚瞓瞓吓聽到有人做愛嘅聲 <br />\n<br />\n我咪以為我細佬睇av囉(人有需求人之常情 所謂食色性也)<br />\n<br />\n咁我都唔理啦 因為小妹都已經好攰！<br />\n<br />\n直至今朝出房門，我尖叫咗一聲<br />\n<br />\n我居然見到我父母赤裸裸咁瞓咗喺梳化，我重見到地下有condom<br />\n<br />\n我嗰刻真係喊咗出嚟，佢哋點可以咁樣！！<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得好污糟！！佢哋係我父母嚟㗎！點可以做埋哩啲事！<br />\n<br />\n我接受唔到！我唔知點去面對佢哋！我覺得佢哋好核突。"},{"pid":"47d900d1b93fcca51e07795beba1c448c60219eb","tid":585630,"uid":38293,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"好污糟！<br />\n<br />\n我諗我哩幾晚都唔會返去！"},{"pid":"b78282774dce5156630b00e7bc7d7614db4b9429","tid":585630,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"咁唔該你以後都唔好扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我出返去先。"},{"pid":"d4f264e2fe7601312aff1ef90e28dfd46df62800","tid":585630,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78282774dce5156630b00e7bc7d7614db4b9429","tid":585630,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"咁唔該你以後都唔好扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我出返去先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"41ff489a1199a7ad731f7f4b05b0726f4d42eb04","tid":585630,"uid":39701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:21:51.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1b7c3b86258393b45a889d6b55ebad2075cc8cf6","tid":585630,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41ff489a1199a7ad731f7f4b05b0726f4d42eb04","tid":585630,"uid":39701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201